    public class CompositeProduct
extends MenuItem
    CompositeProduct is the second main entity we'll be using to do different operations on the delivery app composed of base products
    Author:
    Szekely Maria-Robertha
    See Also:

    The getters of this class compute the actual value of rating, calories, etc. based on the list of baseproducts\, Serialized Form
